# =============================================================================
# ALLOWED EXCEPTIONS (Whitelist)
# =============================================================================
# Note: If you need to commit ANY of the above, use:
# git add -f file_name.ext
# But NEVER do this for credentials/secrets!

# =============================================================================
# DOCUMENTATION
# =============================================================================

# SAFE TO COMMIT:
# ✅ .tf files (Terraform code)
# ✅ .yml/.yaml files (without credentials)
# ✅ .md files (documentation)
# ✅ .sh files (scripts without secrets)
# ✅ Terraform outputs (without sensitive data)

# DO NOT COMMIT:
# ❌ .tfstate files
# ❌ .pem / .key files
# ❌ .env files
# ❌ Credentials of any kind
# ❌ SSH private keys
# ❌ Any file with passwords/tokens
